column2: SELECT u.up_col0 as [col0],     &&& + cast(x.objId as varchar(#)) + &&&+ cast(x.objId as varchar(#)) + &&& as objID, p.ra, p.dec,     p.petroR5#_r, p.petroR9#_r,    s.specObjID, s.z FROM #upload u       JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id       JOIN PhotoObjAll p ON p.objID = x.objID       JOIN SpecObjAll s ON p.objID = s.bestObjID ORDER by x.up_id
